short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Extract Channel ID for any Youtube channel in one click.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A quick little tool that lets you easily view and copy the channel ID of any YouTube channel. 

This is especially useful because YouTube now supports custom username in URLs, so getting channel ID is difficult for non-technical folks.
